cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper deals with domain adaptation using deep learning techniques, which is a common topic in the sub-fields of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE). However, since the paper focuses on using a Monte Carlo dropout based ensemble discriminator, which is a specific technique used in deep learning, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
